snippet.title: Crystal Comet (steam game) announcement trailer!
snippet.description:
Crystal comet is an old-school chaotic twin stick space shoot em' up. You are not the hero - you're part of a squad! - Play single player with the AI or drop in / drop out local co-op!

Now available on Steam.

Wesbsite: https://crystalcomet.net/

Store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2642920/Crystal_Comet/

A game by RewdanSprites. 
Music by Paul Michael Kixx. (also music in game).
Level background designs by Mavy Orion. 
Trailer thumbnail & marketing art by Curz Blayz.
